snippet.title: Cryptobots Gameplay
snippet.description:
Fight to earn
Assemble Bots and Spaceships into squads and dominate PvP arenas to earn BITS and OIL tokens!
Produce, Sell and Rent out
All Bots, Ships, and Lands are in-game NFTs owned by the players who earn by producing, renting, and playing them.
Unite and Earn more
Cooperative features unique to the p2e market — unite in Alliances to take your earnings to a bigger scale!
Grow Your Empire to Earn
Develop your economic strategy — utilize your NFT Lands to earn profits by producing resources, providing services, and more!
Stake to Earn
BITS token holders can stake their tokens to receive more $BITS!

https://cryptobots.me/
